data.enText: a unit for measuring length; a 1 000th of a metre

tr: a metric unit of length equal to one thousandth of a meter

value.boxr_value: in AM, use 美国英语用 millimeter

value.def: A millimetre is a metric unit of length that is equal to a tenth of a centimetre or a thousandth of a metre.

example.ex: ...a tiny little transparent pill, about 20 millimetres long.
example.tran: 大约20毫米长的透明小药片
